{"tid":1211622,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"紅底耀中幼教賣學生 企硬要學生613準時經金鐘中環返學校考試","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:36:06.000Z","uid":147392,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72ae407ffd80928f9d8a9316638638c6b8872896","tid":1211622,"uid":147392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"有個讀耀中幼教學院(YCCECE)嘅朋友send黎<br />\n<br />\n今日警方開左槍之後大約17:30收到學校email同SMS表示原定聽日嘅考試會如常進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEG0cuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEG0cuH.png&h=8f5e05f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQJJUH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQJJUH2.png&h=e76d159f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校好明確要佢地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日如常準時考試，並預留時間到校</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無話彈性處理，連叫啲學生小心啲都無</span><br />\n<br />\n佢地有同學Whatsapp問學校職員詢問事件，<span style=\"color: red;\">職員</span>表示學校係為左學生前途所以安排如常考試<br />\n哦！原來作為學校，<span style=\"color: red;\">學生嘅考試前途係大於人身安全</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJSVLRp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJSVLRp.png&h=22e6bbf7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZNR3C5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZNR3C5.png&h=c1a2140b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5Lz1pM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5Lz1pM.png&h=378bcafa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQD574N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQD574N.png&h=b9ed52e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家岀面咁嘅情況，佢地有啲同學發緊夢，其他好多都無心情温書<br />\n<br />\n唔講政治因素，學校都完全莫視學生聽日返校安全，間學校喺田灣，大部分搭地鐵到校嘅學生都要經金鐘站轉車，有啲巴士都要經中環，喺依個非常時期學校仲要佢地番學，傻的嗎，早啲起身行返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  考十點住屯門上水嗰啲應該幾點出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲講到關心學生前途所以先如常考試，考試&gt;香港發生嘅事+人生安全，作為一間培育幼教老師嘅辦學團體咁樣去&rdquo;身教&rdquo;未來老師，真係好為學生嘅未來著想，為香港嘅未來著想咩？<br />\n<br />\nFYI 耀中幼教學院同耀中國際幼稚園係同一辦學團體，咁樣妄顧香港同學生安全嘅學校，香港咁嘅環境都要學生温書，準時去考試，喺幼稚園佢地會教左啲咩小朋友岀黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得叫想讀幼教嘅人揀呢間嚟讀！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />